column5: I've been using it for less than a week and I'm happy with the product. The material is soft and the outer surface looks glossy. It's good for mild to moderate, Bangalore winters. It's especially just right for the current cool, rainy weather. For colder weather it's good to combine it with a cotton blanket (which I tried). That keeps you really warm and toasty. Haven't washed it yet. I may do an update once I've given it a wash. The one minor downside is that it slightly irritates my neck ...
